What you need to know:

The 2022 Awcon will double up as the qualifiers for the 2023 Women’s World Cup that will be hosted jointly by Australia and New ZealandThe semi-finalists at the prestigious continental showpiece will gain automatic qualification to the Women’s World CupWinners of the first-round matches of the 2022 Awcon qualifiers, which will be played in two legs, will advance to the second round of the qualifiers